tps://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/671220826/image_671220826.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/671220826/image_671220826.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/671220826/image_671220826.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">suteishi/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Investing in a turnaround play can be incredibly profitable. This is because shares of the business can rise spectacularly once the picture starts improving. On the other hand, it's also fraught with risks. For starters, if the business does not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/671220826/image_671220826.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741668-signet-jewelers-q3-preview-why-granting-management-the-benefit-of-the-doubt", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 12:18:01"}, {"id": "4741673", "title": "Major Asset Classes: November 2024 Performance Review", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Black calendar sheet for November 2024 with thumbtack on wooden board, Position with copy space.\" data-id=\"2176548729\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">southtownboy/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Global markets delivered mixed results in November. US stocks and real estate investment trusts led last month's winners, rebounding with solid gains following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732147-major-asset-classes-october-2024-performance-review\" rel=\"noopener\">October's decline,</a> based on a set of ETFs. Commodities and shares in emerging markets</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2176548729/image_2176548729.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741673-major-asset-classes-november-2024-performance-review", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 12:10:00"}, {"id": "4741671", "title": "UTF And RLTY: Quality Infrastructure And Real Estate Looking Attractive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money on the edge\" data-id=\"1445810122\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"986px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Written by Nick Ackerman</em></p> <p>Infrastructure and real estate are two areas the world needs to function, at least function with some comfort and efficiency. Cohen Steers Infrastructure Fund (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UTF\" title=\"Cohen&amp;Steers Infrastructure Fund\">UTF</a>) and Cohen &amp; Steers Real Estate Opportunities and Income</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810122/image_1445810122.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741671-utf-and-rlty-quality-infrastructure-and-real-estate-looking-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4741663", "title": "Old CEO Out, 'New CEO' In - Struggling Intel Is A Bargain Nonetheless", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Headquarters\" data-id=\"1831946092\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1831946092/image_1831946092.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span class=\"highlighted_text\">In my last few articles about Intel Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC:CA\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC:CA</a></span>), I was always</span> bullish, and I don\u2019t want to justify myself here in any way. I was clearly wrong a